    "body": "I had a quick look, and it seems that os.system has problems with network shares, which forced us into the convoluted dance present in `utils.process`.  That probably came from bug reports, it's not something that we can easily test without setting up a windows environment with network drives...\n\nJust a data point from a quick look at the code, I didn't actually dig very deep.\n"
